About
Enjoy a Rewarding “Second Act” in Sunny Florida
If you’d like to renew your zest for life in sunny Florida, begin by planting your roots in Southway Villa Manufactured Housing Community in Brooksville, Florida. Nature abounds on property with 4 scenic ponds, grassy lawns, and gorgeous, mature shade trees. Our 272 single-wide and double-wide homes on 46.5 acres are superbly maintained, and our wide, paved streets allow for safety and east of access.
end column
end container
end section
Option-1:
Option-2:
start Slider JS
start builder section
start container
start column
Area Features
A world away from the hubbub and high prices of other Florida destinations, Brooksville/Wachee offers a myriad of authentic experiences. Florida’s Adventure Coast boasts plenty of scenic waterways brimming with life and beauty. Stroll along historic streets and be charmed by our local culture. Reel in the thrills with onshore and saltwater fishing, canoeing, kayaking, or an exciting excursion to the Gulf of Mexico. Plus, you can take a leisure drive to Tampa in under an hour’s time!
Enjoy excellent local healthcare with over 37 hospitals/medical centers within the greater Brooksville area. So, reward yourself with the best life has to offer!
end column
